Dear Hiring Team,

I am writing to apply for the Batch Developer (UNIX/C/SQL) role with Gainwell Technologies. I bring over three years of experience building and supporting production backend systems, SQL-heavy data services, and long-running job orchestration, along with a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University.

